
- if @constituencies.empty?
  %h2 We couldn't find anything
  = "Sorry! We couldn't find any divisions lists when searching for <em>" + @params[:q] + "</em>."
  %p You may find a division if you search again using a longer word.
- else
  %p= "You searched for <em>" + @params[:q] + "</em>." 
  %p The following division lists contain that text:
  %ol.search-results
    - @constituencies.each do |link|
      %li
        %a{ :href => "/divisions/number/#{link}" }= "Division #{link}"
        = link.inspect
    